174
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:53,810
Wherever Sansan is, that's where I'll be.

175
00:10:56,360 --> 00:10:57,440
Come with me.

176
00:10:57,680 --> 00:10:58,740
Where are we going?

177
00:11:00,040 --> 00:11:01,240
Welcome, Xu Sansan,

178
00:11:01,560 --> 00:11:03,400
to beautiful Xinjiang.

179
00:11:04,800 --> 00:11:06,200
